ancy. From family members to colleagues, strangers to friend',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(154,'2025-08-03 04:50:16.154776','28','Pregnancy is often described as a life-changing journey for a woman ‚Äî a mix of emotions, physical transformations, and evolving roles. But while a lot of attention is focused on the expectant mother, ',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(155,'2025-08-03 04:50:40.941842','27','Pregnancy is often described as a miracle, a beautiful journey, or the most rewarding time in a woman‚Äôs life. While that may be true, there‚Äôs another reality that many women silently go through: the e',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(156,'2025-08-03 04:51:34.923156','26','Your guide to a safe, healthy, and joyful pregnancy journey<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPregnancy is a magical and transformative journey, but it‚Äôs also one that comes with significant responsibility. As a woman carry',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(157,'2025-08-03 04:51:55.177610','25','Pregnancy is one of the most profound journeys a woman can experience. It is a time of joy, anticipation, transformation, and tremendous responsibility. From the moment I learned that I was carrying a',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(158,'2025-08-03 04:55:10.815162','24','The moment your baby is born, everything changes ‚Äî physically, emotionally, and mentally. It\'s not just the beginning of motherhood, but also the start of a powerful and unpredictable journey of recov',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(159,'2025-08-03 04:55:53.089443','23','The postpartum period, often referred to as the ‚Äúfourth trimester,‚Äù is a deeply sensitive and transformative time for a mother. It‚Äôs marked by physical healing, emotional vulnerability, and a steep le',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(160,'2025-08-03 04:56:16.910006','22','Pregnancy is often described as a journey ‚Äî one filled with emotional highs, physical changes, and profound anticipation. But what is often less spoken about is the confusing, vulnerable phase that fo',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(161,'2025-08-03 04:56:34.151123','21','Pregnancy is a journey filled with dreams, anticipation, and a growing love for the child within. But the true transformation ‚Äî the one that quietly reshapes a woman forever ‚Äî often begins after child',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(162,'2025-08-03 04:57:10.905626','20','The first three months after childbirth ‚Äî often referred to as the fourth trimester ‚Äî are unlike any other phase of life. These early postpartum days are not just about taking care of a newborn; they ',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(163,'2025-08-03 04:57:31.759570','19','Returning to work after giving birth is a deeply personal and complex decision that is influenced by many factors ‚Äî physical recovery, emotional readiness, financial needs, workplace policies, and the',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(164,'2025-08-03 04:57:54.345097','18','Welcoming a new baby into the world is a transformative experience, and maternity leave offers a much-needed pause from the professional world to heal, bond, and adjust to this profound life change. B',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(165,'2025-08-03 04:58:16.317467','17','Becoming a parent is life-changing in ways we cannot always anticipate. From sleepless nights and endless diaper changes to emotional swings and overwhelming love, parenthood is a whirlwind. Ideally, ',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(166,'2025-08-03 04:58:38.846541','16','Returning to the workplace after giving birth is a powerful and often emotional milestone in a woman‚Äôs life. It‚Äôs more than just resuming a job ‚Äî it‚Äôs navigating a transformed identity, adjusting to n',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(167,'2025-08-03 04:59:10.237983','15','Becoming a new mother is one of life‚Äôs most profound transitions. It brings joy, love, and purpose ‚Äî but also responsibility, exhaustion, and a complete reshuffling of priorities. For many women, the ',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(168,'2025-08-03 17:13:31.635085','17','Becoming a parent is life-changing in ways we cannot always anticipate. From sleepless nights and endless diaper changes to emotional swings and overwhelming love, parenthood is a whirlwind. Ideally, ',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',10,4),(169,'2025-08-03 17:17:25.914861','16','Returning to the workplace after giving birth is a powerful and often emotional milestone in a woman‚Äôs life. It‚Äôs more than just resuming a job ‚Äî it‚Äôs navigating a transformed identity, adjusting to n',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Question\"]}}]',10,4),(170,'2025-08-03 17:18:40.113431','19','Returning to work after giving birth is a deeply personal and complex decision that is influenced by many factors ‚Äî physical recovery, emotional readiness, financial needs, workplace policies, and the',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Question\"]}}]',10,4),(171,'2025-08-03 17:21:27.410648','28','When did you return to work post child birth? What do you think is the right time to return back to work? Read about what other moms are saying about this!e!',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',7,4),(172,'2025-08-03 17:22:16.818580','31','What are the different challenges you faced in work space post childbirth? See what other moms are talking about this more!',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',7,4),(173,'2025-08-03 17:42:27.133147','28','When did you return to work post child birth? What do you think is the right time to return back to work? Read about what other moms are saying about this!',2,'[{\"changed\": {\"fields\": [\"Body\"]}}]',7,4),(174,'2025-08-03 18:24:01.602518','52','hi',3,'',7,4),(175,'2025-08-11 18:00:04.756646','4','Suvarna Hegde',2,'