INSERT INTO `spotlight_womeninspotlight` VALUES (3,'Sridevi Pujar','profile_pictures/user.png','Mrs. Sridevi Pujar (62 years), also known as Jayamma, is the embodiment of resilience,\r\nselflessness, and quiet strength. Born into a prosperous family that lost everything due to\r\nunexpected government laws, she rose above adversity with sheer determination. Earning a\r\ncollege degree through scholarship, she balanced academics with household chores and\r\nbecame a pillar of support for her five siblings‚Äîemotionally, mentally, and financially. Even\r\nas a young girl, she worked part-time to keep her family afloat. Married at an early age, she\r\nextended her strength and compassion to her husband‚Äôs family, becoming their emotional\r\nanchor and financial backbone. She gave her all‚Äîphysically, emotionally, and mentally‚Äîto\r\nuplift those around her, never asking for anything in return. In a world that often overlooks\r\nquiet strength, Sridevi‚Äôs journey is a tribute to every woman who rises despite the odds, who\r\nturns adversity into opportunity, and who builds futures from fragments of the past. Her life\r\nis not just a story of survival‚Äîit‚Äôs a legacy of courage, compassion, and indomitable\r\nwillpower that continues to inspire generations. Today, after a lifetime of giving, Sridevi is\r\nfinally channeling her passion and hard work into something of her own‚Äîcrafting homemade\r\ndry fruit laddoos that are not only delicious but packed with health benefits. Each bite tells a\r\nstory of tradition, purity, and love‚Äîthe same values she has lived by. Her laddoos are made\r\nwith care, using the finest ingredients, and are a perfect blend of nourishment and taste. This\r\nnew chapter is not just a business‚Äîit‚Äôs her legacy in motion. Contact us to get in touch with\r\nSridevi and place your order for these wholesome, mouthwatering laddoos. Taste the\r\nstrength. Share the story.'),(4,'Suvarna Hegde','profile_pictures/user_j97PBtv.png','Mrs. Suvarna Hegde‚Äôs life is a moving testament to courage, dignity, and relentless\r\ndetermination. Born into a humble family and educated through a government school, her\r\nearly years were marked by limited resources but unlimited inner strength. Married and\r\ndivorced at a young age, she found herself alone‚Äîbut far from broken. With a brave heart\r\nand unshakable resolve, she single-handedly raised her daughter, determined to give her a life\r\nof possibilities. Every challenge only made her stronger, and her sacrifices bore fruit‚Äîher\r\ndaughter now thrives as a professional at Texas University, USA, a reflection of Suvarna‚Äôs\r\nunwavering dedication and love. Refusing to rely on fate, Suvarna built her livelihood\r\nthrough hard work and self-reliance. Today, she crafts fresh, crunchy banana and potato\r\nchips‚Äîhomemade with care, quality, and authenticity. Every packet holds more than\r\nflavor‚Äîit holds a story of perseverance, pride, and empowerment. Suvarna‚Äôs life reminds us\r\nthat success isn‚Äôt measured by wealth, but by the courage to rise when life knocks you down.\r\nLet‚Äôs celebrate her spirit by celebrating her venture. Contact us today to order her delicious,\r\nhome-style chips‚Äîand become a part of her incredible journey from hardship to hope.');
